description: Barcode Professional SDK for .NET Core can be used for adding advanced barcode image generation to any .NET Core-based applications, including ASP.NET CORE projects. Features: - Linear, Postal & 2D Barcode Symbologies - Generate barcode images in many formats like GIF, BMP, PNG, JPEG-JPG, SVG and more formats with Rotation support - GS1, ISO/IEC & AIM Spec Compliance - Supported Barcodes - Australia Post 4-state Barcode, ABC Codabar, USS Code 128 A-B-C, USS Code 39, USS Code 93, Data Matrix ECC200, Deutsche Post Identcode, Deutsche Post Leitcode, EAN-13, GTIN-13, EAN-8, GTIN-8, EAN-99, Coupon Barcode, EAN-Velocity, Industrial 2 of 5, Standard 2 of 5, Interleaved 2 of 5, ITF 25, ISBN, Bookland EAN, ISBN-13, ISBN-10, ISMN, ISSN, ITF-14, EAN-14, DUN-14, GTIN-14, JAN-13, JAN-8, MSI, OPC, PDF417, Portable Data File 417, PDF417 Truncated, PLANET, POSTNET, PZN, British Royal Mail 4-State Customer Barcode, RM4SCC, Royal TPG Post KIX 4-State Barcode, SCC-14, Singapore 4-State Postal Code Barcode, SSCC-18, UPC-128, EAN-18, Swiss PostParcel Barcode, UCC-EAN-128, EAN-128, GTIN-128, UPC-A, UPC-E, GTIN-12, USPS Sack Label, USPS Tray Label Barcode, QR Code, USPS FIM, USPS Horizontal Bars, Telepen, Pharmacode, Semacode, Code 32 Italian Pharmacode IMH, USPS Package Identification Code (PIC), FedEx Ground 96, HIBC LIC/PAS, ISBT 128, Italian Post 25, USPS Intelligent Mail Barcode, VICS BOL, VICS Bill of Lading, VICS SCAC PRO, Aztec Code, Compact PDF417, Macro PDF417, Micro PDF417, Micro QR Code, UPS MaxiCode, GS1 DataBar, RSS-14, Matrix 2 of 5, Danish Postal 39, French Postal 39 A/R, GS1 DataMatrix, ALL EAN.UCC Composite Barcodes CC-A, CC-B, CC-C, USPS Intelligent Mail Container Barcode, Han Xin Code, Japan Post 4state, Korea Post, Datalogic
summary: Barcode Professional SDK for .NET Core can be used for adding advanced barcode image generation to any .NET Core-based applications, including ASP.NET CORE projects.
title: Barcode Professional SDK for .NET Core & ASP.NET Core
